          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Social Security Benefit Payments Choice Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill allows a&nbsp;recipient of monthly Old Age,&nbsp;Survivors,&nbsp;and Disability Insurance benefits,&nbsp;unless the&nbsp;recipient is&nbsp;concurrently entitled to Supplemental Security Income benefits, to choose the day of the month upon which to receive such benefits. <br /></p> <p><br /></p>]]></text>
